                            <div class="content-area row">

                        <header class="col-sm-12 title-row">
        <h1>The Bit: How KFAN became America’s dominant sports radio station</h1>
        <span class="byline">

            Wednesday, February 13, 2019
      
                              by <a href="http://www.citypages.com/about/staff/jay-boller/372121392" title="Jay Boller">Jay Boller</a>
  
      in <a href="http://www.citypages.com/news" title="News">News</a>
  
</span>
    </header>

                    <div class="col-sm-12 table-block">
                        <div class="left-col">

                                <div class="article-block">
                <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12">

                                        <img src="http://stmedia.stimg.co/ctyp-news-021319-KFAN-Bruce-Kluckhohn.jpg?w=800" alt="From left: Dan “Common Man” Cole, Cory Cove, Chris Hawkey, Dan Barreiro, Paul Allen, and Paul “Meatsauce” Lambert" class="intro-image" />
    <p class="row ">
                    <span class="caption col-sm-8">From left: Dan “Common Man” Cole, Cory Cove, Chris Hawkey, Dan Barreiro, Paul Allen, and Paul “Meatsauce” Lambert</span>
                            <span class="caption col-sm-4 align-right">Bruce Kluckhohn</span>
            </p>
                
                

